{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/man-city-game-experience/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"My ideas' home"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"d08f87ac-d7a6-59a8-ba24-6fbda8343d46","excerpt":"I had been dreaming about visiting the Etihad Stadium one day in my life. When I first applied for the Chevening Scholarship, watching a Mancity game was one of…","html":"<p>I had been dreaming about visiting the Etihad Stadium one day in my life. When I first applied for the Chevening Scholarship, watching a Mancity game was one of the reasons why I wanted to come to the UK. </p>\n<p>I knew Boxing Day was a big day for the English Premier League, which is why I booked my ticket for the Manchester City against Leicester Game despite fear of postponement due to the new variant of COVID. </p>\n<p>I traveled from Colchester to Manchester on the 24th of December and, I booked my stay at the Britannica Hotel in the heart of Manchester Piccadilly. </p>\n<p>On the day of the game,  I took the bus to the Stadium. At first glimpse of the Stadium, I was in tears. My childhood dream became a reality. I was at the Etihad Stadium.</p>\n<p>I arrived a bit late and missed the chance to have a full official Stadium tour. I still managed to visit the Stadium by myself later on, and took some nice pictures. </p>\n<h3>Meeting the legend</h3>\n<p>Firstly, let’s start with a bit of history. I have been supporting Manchester City since 2008 when I found that Vincent Kompany has some Congolese origin and comes from the same region as I. I wish I had the chance to meet him when he played for ManCity, but sadly he retired from professional football years ago. </p>\n<p>I have been a massive fan of him for his leadership on and off the pitch. I consider him my role model; therefore, I had to take my first picture of the day with his statue. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1bd6302d891c4d12fca12010f183eba9/9568a/meeting-the-legend.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.1081081081081%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"legend\"\n        title=\"legend\"\n        src=\"/static/1bd6302d891c4d12fca12010f183eba9/1c72d/meeting-the-legend.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1bd6302d891c4d12fca12010f183eba9/a80bd/meeting-the-legend.jpg 148w,\n/static/1bd6302d891c4d12fca12010f183eba9/1c91a/meeting-the-legend.jpg 295w,\n/static/1bd6302d891c4d12fca12010f183eba9/1c72d/meeting-the-legend.jpg 590w,\n/static/1bd6302d891c4d12fca12010f183eba9/a8a14/meeting-the-legend.jpg 885w,\n/static/1bd6302d891c4d12fca12010f183eba9/fbd2c/meeting-the-legend.jpg 1180w,\n/static/1bd6302d891c4d12fca12010f183eba9/9568a/meeting-the-legend.jpg 3024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>The Dream come true</h3>\n<p>Secondly, I went to the Stadium and took the picture that sums up my childhood dreams, Espoir in the UK.</p>\n<p><img src=\"./images/etihad-stadium.jpeg\" alt=\"at Stadium\"></p>\n<h3>Cream on the cake, I watched a game live.</h3>\n<p>And Finally, before the game, I took another one to show people and everyone I have been watching football with in Goma, Bukavu, Kigali pubs that their friend and the only Manchester City fan they know has made it to the Stadium. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/892ee9f924b9dc02955fd3860ea8275e/9568a/before-game.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.1081081081081%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"before the game\"\n        title=\"before the game\"\n        src=\"/static/892ee9f924b9dc02955fd3860ea8275e/1c72d/before-game.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/892ee9f924b9dc02955fd3860ea8275e/a80bd/before-game.jpg 148w,\n/static/892ee9f924b9dc02955fd3860ea8275e/1c91a/before-game.jpg 295w,\n/static/892ee9f924b9dc02955fd3860ea8275e/1c72d/before-game.jpg 590w,\n/static/892ee9f924b9dc02955fd3860ea8275e/a8a14/before-game.jpg 885w,\n/static/892ee9f924b9dc02955fd3860ea8275e/fbd2c/before-game.jpg 1180w,\n/static/892ee9f924b9dc02955fd3860ea8275e/9568a/before-game.jpg 3024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Final result and FPL disappointments</h3>\n<p>The game did end up well; we won 6-3; unfortunately, my FPL captain Phil Foden got only one point. I think this is the old FPL course. You_ should not captain a player you will be watching live. _</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4a97b175dd93ec278fe046489e4cb90d/ec605/fpl-team-result.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 216.2162162162162%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"fpl team result\"\n        title=\"fpl team result\"\n        src=\"/static/4a97b175dd93ec278fe046489e4cb90d/1c72d/fpl-team-result.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4a97b175dd93ec278fe046489e4cb90d/a80bd/fpl-team-result.jpg 148w,\n/static/4a97b175dd93ec278fe046489e4cb90d/1c91a/fpl-team-result.jpg 295w,\n/static/4a97b175dd93ec278fe046489e4cb90d/1c72d/fpl-team-result.jpg 590w,\n/static/4a97b175dd93ec278fe046489e4cb90d/a8a14/fpl-team-result.jpg 885w,\n/static/4a97b175dd93ec278fe046489e4cb90d/ec605/fpl-team-result.jpg 1125w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>I wish I had the chance to catch the Canal + Broadcasting car to get a chance to pass on TV, but unfortunately, I couldn’t find where the car was standing.</p>\n<p>Now I can say that I finished my year in style. I hope to watch more games in the future and more importantly to catch the CANAL + car next time I visit the Stadium.  </p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Local Boy visited the Etihad Stadium. Here is how it went.","date":"27 December, 2021","description":"Boxing Day is an important day in the premier league season; hence as a Manchester City supporter Espoir Murhabazi relates about his experience watching a Premier League game live in Manchester.","cover_image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":0.75,"src":"/static/86c641c6c3b743d87cba95dded2df2a8/a6352/dream-come-true.jpg","srcSet":"/static/86c641c6c3b743d87cba95dded2df2a8/40426/dream-come-